{
  "stem": "12413.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The life in ghetto was very harsh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have rationed food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Living in dilapidated housing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No plumbing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The young, who are trying to obtain life certificates, you know, like to work in certain places.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The old couldn't do it for obvious reasons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because you-- when you are 50 or 45, you couldn't go to into a any German office and ask for-- for a job.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From time to time, the German entered the ghetto, rounding up people just at random, and taking them away for execution, or just sending them away to Treblinka, or to other places.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I mean the number of the Jews were diminishing constantly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But some were trying to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but the life was very, I wouldn't say dull, but it was a life when you live in certain fear.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you live in terror.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When you expect something to happen-- something like a miracle, or a quick end to the war, which that never happened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was the atmosphere in-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Total despair.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were depressed, who were meeting each other you know, sad, and knowing that something awful will happen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was also a big problem, because we knew [INAUDIBLE] there were sick people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I would say there were less sick people-- I don't recall-- I mean-- my neighbor, or my friends, or my relatives being sick.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if you went into the hospital, the German liquidated the hospital when they went into the hospital, and they took the sick people away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So people are very leery to go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they tried to stay home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were doctors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were doctors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not too many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they eliminated a lot of doctors when they invaded the town.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
